What you need to know:

Kenya are in Pool ‘A’ alongside hosts Japan, Serbia, Brazil, Korea and Dominican Republic and Bitok believes he has a squad capable of staging an upset in TokyoExperienced pair of middle blocker Violet Makuto and libero Elizabeth Wanyama were the surprise omissions in the final squad of 12Skipper Mercy Moim, her assistant Noel Murambi, evergreen setter Jane Wacu and Edith Wisa are some of the experienced players in the team